title: Grateful Dead Live at Ice Stadium on 1990-10-13
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.8 MHz) >KORG AudioGate 4 > Adobe Audition CC 2015 > Samplitude Pro X3 Suite > FLAC/24
description:
Set 1

Cold Rain & Snow, Feel Like A Stranger, Candyman, Walkin' Blues, Loser, Queen Jane Approximately, Bird Song, Promised Land

Set 2

Touch Of Gray, Estimated Prophet-> Crazy Fingers-> Playin' In The Band-> Drums-> Jam-> All Along The Watchtower-> Stella Blue-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: One More Saturday Night

reviews.review_text:
Great little show here The Dead's sole foray in to Sweden, and a magnificent 24 bit Charlie Miller soundboard to boot.
Thanks.
